attachments.displayName: They were in a temple once. Today they were on a wall, among scattered leaves. And yet, they looked amazingly serene, and full of dignity. Our Cell Shutterbugs Daily Snap - Lord Ganesh and Goddess Lakshmi on a wall in Mayur Vihar. Captured in brilliant detail using a Lumia 1020. More on the picture here: http://www.cellshutterbugs.com/2013/11/cell-shutterbugs-daily-snap-15-gods-on.html
